HEADWORD: left brain
<hw>left" brain`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The left cerebral hemisphere
of the brain; in humans, it controls motor activity on the right side of
the body, and in most people is the primary location for control of
language, logic, and mathematical thought.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

